Package: condlSample
Type: Package
Title: Generate random samples from the assumed error distribution of a 
    regression model, conditional on predictor variable values.
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Date: 2017-03-04
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Hagemann", email = "mark.hagemann@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Mark Hagemann <mark.hagemann@gmail.com>
Description: Contains functions for generating samples from linear models and rating-curve 
    models specified in the rcmodel package (which shares a common origin with these functions)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests:
    testthat,
    rcmodel
Imports:
    markstats
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
